---
title: Strolling Rigatoni with Cherry Tomatoes and Mozzarella
description: The key to this dish is gently roasting the cherry tomatoes and pepper to bring out their natural sweetness and then balancing this against tangy olives and mild, creamy mozzarella. We’ve made it super quick and easy, to leave more time for putting your feet up!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/strolling-rigatoni-with-cherry-tomatoes-b714641e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/strolling-rigatoni-with-cherry-t-525a6b3e.pdf
